{"type":"message","id":"92212be7","parentId":"d198e27b","timestamp":"2026-04-24T06:39:47.116Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户同意让我把公告内容拉出来整理成表。我需要访问这些招标公告的PDF/文档链接来获取详细内容。从之前的结果中，我可以看到一些文件名的模式：\n\n- https://www.lwty.com/News_lists_sort_33.shtml 是招标采购页面\n- 文件名格式如 \"四川里伍铜业股份有限公司里伍铜矿井下供电系统高低压配电柜设备采购及安装项目招标公告.pdf\"\n- URL格式可能是 /Upload/... 路径\n\n让我尝试访问这些具体的公告文档。\n\n从HTML中我可以看到文件链接模式，但实际URL需要拼接。\n\n我需要先列出所有可整理的公告项目，然后逐个获取详细内容来提取关键信息。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的，我先整理一下所有可以提取详细内容的招标公告和文件：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"847649369","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -sL --connect-timeout 10 --max-time 30 \"https://www.lwty.com/News_lists_sort_37.shtml\" | sed 's/<[^>]*>//g' | tr -d '\\n\\r' | head -6000","timeout":45}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":55755,"output":405,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56160,"cost":{"input":0.11151,"output":0.00486,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11637}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777012777917,"responseId":"chatcmpl-lknc6ytvre8hx5cj5a9h7f"}}
